	<h2><TMPL_VAR NAME="PAGE_TITLE"> Tips</h2>
	<p><strong>Need to verify or identify current coverage? With Carrier DiscoverySM, you can identify critical insurance carrier information on claimants and other involved parties in an accident. Carrier Discovery provides policy data on private passenger auto policies through a name and address or VIN search.</strong></p>

	<p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>Search methods include:</p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p><b>VIN only-</b></p>
	<p>Required fields are VIN and Claim #. Providing data in more fields increases the reliability of your search. You must enter information in the required fields.</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p><b>-- OR --</b></p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p><b>Name and Address-</b></p>
	<p>Required fields are Claims #, Last Name, First Name, Street Name, City, State & Zip.  For optimal results House #, SSN, Driver License # & State should be populated.</p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<p>Please see the <a style="cursor: help;" href="javascript:void(0);" onClick="open_help('carrier_discovery_help.html');"><u><b>Help Page</b></u></a> for much more information on how to best utilize this powerful report.</p>
